[See this thesis: Hoch SL. The Social Consequences of Soviet Immunization Policies, 1945-1980. University of Iowa. The National Council for Eurasian and East European Research. https://www.ucis.pitt.edu/nceeer/1997-812-03g-Hoch.pdf for background on Soviet immunization policy, perhaps explaining current vaccine hesitancy in the US of people of Russian origin. - Mod.LK]

